      "source": [
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
        "\n",
        "# Simulated Red & NIR bands\n",
        "np.random.seed(0)\n",
        "red = np.random.randint(50, 200, (50, 50)).astype('float32')\n",
        "nir = np.random.randint(100, 255, (50, 50)).astype('float32')\n",
        "\n",
        "# NDVI calculation\n",
        "ndvi = (nir - red) / (nir + red)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Plot NDVI\n",
        "plt.imshow(ndvi, cmap='RdYlGn')\n",
        "plt.colorbar(label=\"NDVI\")\n",
        "plt.title(\"NDVI Demo (Simulated Data)\")\n",
        "plt.show()"
      ]
    },
